{"tid":1287014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真正要小心嘅係紅黨B隊","createTime":"2019-07-05T04:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T12:40:57.000Z","uid":125499,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b1f8bd3f8b2ec27d22eb6e770409dec25f3764","tid":1287014,"uid":125499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"呢個post會俾好多人屌，預左！但係我都好想俾大家參考一下！泛民某程度俾保皇更賣港！<br />\n<br />\n點解要小心佢地係因為佢地會賣煽情去令我地嘅運動再次失敗！例如上次嘅雨傘出動糾察隊去阻止義士做進一步行動。亦都係口中大家講嘅鄺神！民眾主發大台俾泛民拆！大家可以google一下！真係仲有好多！<br />\n<br />\n再舉多個例子:泛民多年黎進入議會暢通無阻！但係點解紅黨要趕絕梁天琦！連入都唔俾佢入呢？<br />\n<br />\n我地今次嘅運動之可以黎到今時今日係因我地嘅一手建立！無大台！完全係我地自己話事！先可以去到全球關注！<br />\n<br />\n最後，我唔係想同大家散播割蓆！係想同大家講聲真係要小心。我地應該自己話事，唔係俾泛民拉住個鼻走！"},{"pid":"d69ede5a2991715f4ed2c289d1efbabca9e8867f","tid":1287014,"uid":125499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:28:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb2ca75d9208ae0077a7889aaf47987229ff1a9d","tid":1287014,"uid":125499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:12:36.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"3cc4d578c580f156a87ac23e4ee43449d691322b","tid":1287014,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:26:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1095585c7b21dff97435540940b64fbe29f8770d","tid":1287014,"uid":125499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cc4d578c580f156a87ac23e4ee43449d691322b","tid":1287014,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d69ede5a2991715f4ed2c289d1efbabca9e8867f","tid":1287014,"uid":125499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:28:16.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:26:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"所以先去到以家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h